Package: SeqDef
Title: Calculate Sequencing Deficiency Scores for Phylogenetic Trees
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates the SeqDef statistic to quantify the marginal genomic 
    value of individual taxa by weighting the availability of sequence resources 
    in related species using a distance-decay kernel. Includes tools for 
    prioritization and sensitivity analysis.
